{"id": 2476, "title": "Ticket #2476: dprintf overhaul master ticket", "description": "<blockquote>\nThis is the master ticket for the set of dprintf enhancements that are currently underway.  The intent is to have a more flexible and isolated dprintf system.\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>Extract safefile library to allow easier updates.  <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"tktview?tn=2180\" title=\"Have the safe_open library be an external\">#2180</a></span>\n<ul>\n<li>Status: done save for verification that safefile's symbolic link checks are unnecessary on Windows.  This will allow complete syncing of code.  Verification is currently deferred until time permits.\n</li></ul>\n</li><li>Break hard circular dependency between dprintf and config. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2477\" title=\"Break hard circular dependency between dprintf and config\">#2477</a></span>.\n<ul>\n<li>Status: done.\n</li></ul>\n</li><li>Allow dprintf to keep log files open between log writes.  <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2064\" title=\"Allow Condor to keep the file descriptor open between writing logs\">#2064</a></span>.\n<ul>\n<li>Status: done.\n</li></ul>\n</li><li>Convert the internal organization of dprintf information to be based around dprintf output targets instead of dprintf levels.  <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2306\" title=\"Multiple file logging output architecturally brittle\">#2306</a></span>.\n<ul>\n<li>Status: done.\n</li></ul>\n</li><li>Allow Condor to direct debug output to something besides a file.\n<ul>\n<li>Status: Currently in planning stages.</li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2064\" title=\"Allow Condor to keep the file descriptor open between writing logs\">#2064</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAllow Condor to keep the file descriptor open between writing logs</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"tktview?tn=2180\" title=\"Have the safe_open library be an external\">#2180</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nHave the safe_open library be an external</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2306\" title=\"Multiple file logging output architecturally brittle\">#2306</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nMultiple file logging output architecturally brittle</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=2477\" title=\"Break hard circular dependency between dprintf and config\">#2477</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nBreak hard circular dependency between dprintf and config</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"tktview?tn=2626\" title=\"Permit dprintf to log to something besides a file.\">#2626</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nPermit dprintf to log to something besides a file.</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2011-Oct-27 16:1